{"ID":"20220906203707-u90kre3","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906203707-u90kre3","title":"e-1spring","type":"doc","updated":"20220906203707"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203708-uq7plob","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906203708-uq7plob","updated":"20220906203708"}},{"ID":"20220906203709-n4suckn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203709-n4suckn","updated":"20220906203709"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5. 常用框架","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203710-p9p5fac","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203710-p9p5fac","updated":"20220906203710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203711-7rovexv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203711-7rovexv","updated":"20220906203711"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaGuide"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：「Java学习+面试指南」一份涵盖大部分 Java 程序员所需要掌握的核心知识。准备 Java 面试，首选 JavaGuide！","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203712-yxl72f5","Type":"NodeHTMLBlock","Data":"\u003cdiv align=\"center\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://www.yuque.com/docs/share/8a30ffb5-83f3-40f9-baf9-38de68b906dc\"\u003e\n            \u003cimg src=\"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/xingqiu/xingqiu.png\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; width: 850px;\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/Snailclimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGithub\u003c/a\u003e |\n        \u003ca href=\"https://gitee.com/SnailClimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGitee\u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e  \n\u003c/div\u003e","HtmlBlockType":6,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203712-yxl72f5","updated":"20220906203712"}},{"ID":"20220906203713-294rhh3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203713-294rhh3","updated":"20220906203713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.1 Spring","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203714-04xyuns","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203714-04xyuns","updated":"20220906203714"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring 基础","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203715-obkeucm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203715-obkeucm","updated":"20220906203715"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是 Spring 框架?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203716-ckvih92","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203716-ckvih92","updated":"20220906203716"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring 是一款开源的轻量级 Java 开发框架，旨在提高开发人员的开发效率以及系统的可维护性。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203717-qf9knb8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203717-qf9knb8","updated":"20220906203717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们一般说 Spring 框架指的都是 Spring Framework，它是很多模块的集合，使用这些模块可以很方便地协助我们进行开发，比如说 Spring 支持 IoC（Inverse of Control:控制反转） 和 AOP(Aspect-Oriented Programming:面向切面编程)、可以很方便地对数据库进行访问、可以很方便地集成第三方组件（电子邮件，任务，调度，缓存等等）、对单元测试支持比较好、支持 RESTful Java 应用程序的开发。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203718-x9qdq01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203718-x9qdq01","updated":"20220906203718"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/38ef122122de4375abcd27c3de8f60b4.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203719-fo0ygr9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203719-fo0ygr9","updated":"20220906203719"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring 最核心的思想就是不重新造轮子，开箱即用，提高开发效率。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203720-51seyq4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203720-51seyq4","updated":"20220906203720"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring 翻译过来就是春天的意思，可见其目标和使命就是为 Java 程序员带来春天啊！感动！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203721-8fq0jn3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203721-8fq0jn3","updated":"20220906203721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🤐 多提一嘴 ： ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语言的流行通常需要一个杀手级的应用，Spring 就是 Java 生态的一个杀手级的应用框架。"}]},{"ID":"20220906203722-6tepbb7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203722-6tepbb7","updated":"20220906203722"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring 提供的核心功能主要是 IoC 和 AOP。学习 Spring ，一定要把 IoC 和 AOP 的核心思想搞懂！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203723-yz55ol3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203723-yz55ol3","updated":"20220906203723"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203724-hzlnk4i","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203724-hzlnk4i","updated":"20220906203724"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203725-onaf1ht","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203725-onaf1ht","updated":"20220906203725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring 官网：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://spring.io/","TextMarkTextContent":"https://spring.io/"}]}]},{"ID":"202209062037